ucaresystem (4.5.0) trusty; urgency=high

  * Complete rewrite
  * Package rename to ucaresystem
  * Modular system
  * Timeshift integration
  * Rename executable to ucaresystem from ucaresystem-core
  * Automatically reboot system (configurable default is false)
  * Proper integration with polkit and pkexec
  * Use x-terminal-emulator
  * Add remove-old-kernels tool
  * Add color output, Honor NO_COLOR (https://no-color.org/)
  * Better debian packaging
  * Use getopt, add many options
  * Add  man pages
  * Compatible with WSL, don't use pkgexec on ucaresystem script
  * Fix desktop menu file
  * Secure bash scripting
  * Remove obsolete files

